exceptions.exn: In environment base_params : BaseParams one_node_params : OneNodeParams base_params pb_params : PrimaryBackupParams base_params Unable to unify "Permutation all_nodes ?M1637" with "NoDup all_nodes".
In environment base_params : BaseParams one_node_params : OneNodeParams base_params pb_params : PrimaryBackupParams base_params Unable to unify "NoDup []" with "NoDup ([Backup] ++ all_nodes)".

original: apply NoDup_Permutation with (l := all_nodes). - apply NoDup_app_right with (l := [Backup]). apply NoDup_nil. - apply NoDup_app_left with (l' := [Backup]). apply NoDup_cons_iff. split. intros contra; discriminate contra. apply NoDup_nil. - intros x. split; intros H. inversion H. inversion H; subst. left. reflexivity. inversion H.
